<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tech Course Hub - Courses</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #007bff, #00c6ff);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
            background: white;
            color: black;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .course {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #218838;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Explore Tech Courses</h1>
        <p>Master coding, digital literacy, and modern tech skills!</p>

        <div class="course">
            <h2>Web Development Basics</h2>
            <p>Learn HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to build interactive websites.</p>
            <button onclick="alert('Enrolled in Web Development Basics!')">Enroll</button>
        </div>

        <div class="course">
            <h2>Python Programming</h2>
            <p>Start coding with Python, the language of AI and automation.</p>
            <button onclick="alert('Enrolled in Python Programming!')">Enroll</button>
        </div>

        <div class="course">
            <h2>Data Science Essentials</h2>
            <p>Analyze data and learn the fundamentals of data science.</p>
            <button onclick="alert('Enrolled in Data Science Essentials!')">Enroll</button>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>
